鰶字的基本解释

鰶
jì
〔鰶鱼〕体侧扁，银灰色，有黑斑。口小无牙。生活在海洋中。

鰶字的汉语字典释义

[①]［jì］
［《廣韻》子例切，去祭，精。］
(1)鱼名。鱼纲鲱科。体侧扁，长椭圆形，长约二十厘米。背部灰绿色，两侧银白色，具黑斑。口小，无牙。背鳍最后一条延长成丝状。生活在沿海，肉可吃。
(2)见“鰶”。

Chinese dictionary definition of words
[①]［jì］
["Guangyun" sub-case cut, go to sacrifice, fine. ]
(1) The name of the fish. Fish class Herring family. The side of the body is flat, oblong, about 20 cm long. The back is gray-green, and the sides are silver-white with dark spots. The mouth is small and toothless. The last dorsal fin is elongated into filaments. Living on the coast, meat is edible.
(2) See "鰶".
